[genericglass Highball] Serving Glass: Highball With Ice

In Mixing Glass With Ice Add:
1 1/2 oz [genericingredient Scotch] Glenlivet Scotch Whiskey
1 oz [genericingredient Cherry Brandy] Cherry Brandy
1/2 oz Sweet Vermouth
1/2 oz [genericingredient Lemon Juice] Lemon Juice
Shake and Strain
Garnish: Lemon Slice

